t\"><strong class=\"block font-display text-base text-slate-950\">Shifa Global Care</strong><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.18em] text-teal-700\">Solution Limited</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-6 xl:flex\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/treatments\">Treatments</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/hospitals\">Hospitals</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/doctors\">Doctors</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/medical-visa\">Medical Visa</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition hover:text-teal-700\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav><div class=\"hidden items-center gap-4 md:flex\"><a class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a><button class=\"rounded-full bg-teal-700 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-teal-900/20 transition hover:bg-teal-800\">Book consultation</button></div><button class=\"grid size-11 place-items-center rounded-xl border border-slate-200 text-xl md:hidden\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle navigation\">☰</button></div></header><main class=\"pt-20\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-slate-50 py-16 px-6\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><header class=\"max-w-3xl mb-12\"><span class=\"text-teal-700 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4\">OUR CARE SERVICES</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight sm:text-5xl\">End-to-End Medical Travel Facilitation</h1><p class=\"text-base text-slate-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed\">Shifa Global Care coordinates every aspect of your treatment journey in India. From initial specialist case reviews to airport pickups, hotel lodging, and post-discharge follow-ups.</p></header><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-6 mb-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-xl transition cursor-pointer bg-teal-700 text-white shadow-xs\">All</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-xl transition cursor-pointer text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:text-slate-900\">Clinical Care</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-xl transition cursor-pointer text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:text-slate-900\">Logistics &amp; Visas</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-xl transition cursor-pointer text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:text-slate-900\">Support Services</button></div><div class=\"relative max-w-xs w-full\"><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Search services...\" class=\"w-full bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl py-2.5 pl-4 pr-10 text-xs focus:outline-none focus:border-teal-600 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-50 transition\" value=\"\"/><span class=\"absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400 text-sm\">🔍</span></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">🩺</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Medical Consultation &amp; Case Evaluation</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Comprehensive review of medical records by leading clinicians to provide clear treatment recommendations and roadmap guidelines.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Specialist second opinions</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Clinical pathway mapping</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Initial records evaluation</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">🏥</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Hospital &amp; Specialist Selection</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Matching patient requirements with JCI-accredited hospitals and renowned surgeons across major Indian metropolitan areas.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Accredited hospital networks</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Surgeon success-rate audits</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Budget optimization</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">📊</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Treatment Planning &amp; Cost Estimation</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Drafting complete care plans including hospital cost estimations, rehabilitation schedules, and total budget allocations.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Itemized cost sheets</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Priority procedure scheduling</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Timeline planning</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">🛂</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Medical Visa Assistance</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">End-to-end guidance for medical visas (MED &amp; MED-Attendant) including hospital invitation letters and fast-track clearance support.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Visa invitation coordination</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Embassy document review</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Fast-track processing advisory</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">✈️</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Travel &amp; Accommodation Arrangements</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Coordinating flight bookings and vetting nearby hotels or guest houses matching patient recovery constraints and companion needs.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Disability-friendly stays</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Companion lodging vetting</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Flexible flight options</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">🚗</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Airport Reception &amp; Transfers</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">On-arrival pickup and ambulance or private vehicle transfer directly to the hospital or hotel to ensure patient safety and comfort.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Ambulance transfers if required</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Dedicated airport assistants</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Secure transit logistics</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">🗣️</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Interpreter &amp; Language Support</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Overcoming language barriers with dedicated patient coordinators speaking Bangla, English, Hindi, and local dialects.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>On-site interpreters</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Translating medical briefs</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>24/7 care desk access</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">📅</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Appointment Coordination</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Securing priority outpatient consultations, lab tests, and hospital admission queues to reduce unnecessary travel stays.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Zero-wait OPD queues</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Same-day diagnostics schedules</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Follow-up scheduling</span></li></ul></div></article><article class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xs hover:shadow-md transition-all flex flex-col justify-between\"><div><div class=\"size-12 rounded-2xl bg-teal-50 text-teal-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6\">❤️</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Post-Treatment Follow-up</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6\">Continuous coordinate support after returning home, helping transmit diagnostic charts back to the operating surgeon.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 mt-auto\"><h4 class=\"text-2xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3\">Features Included:</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Teleconsultation scheduling</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Prescription renewal guides</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-2xs text-slate-600\"><span class=\"text-teal-700\">✓</span><span>Care continuity audits</span></li></ul></div></article></div><div class=\"mt-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-800 to-cyan-950 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-lg\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_75%_20%,rgba(20,184,166,0.15),transparent_25%)]\"></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-3 relative z-10\">Need Assistance Choosing a Pathway?</h2><p class=\"text-slate-200 text-xs max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6 relative z-10\">Tell us about your diagnostic briefs and treatment goals. A case coordinator will evaluate and estimate costs with leading specialists.</p><button class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-white text-teal-900 font-bold px-6 py-3.5 text-xs shadow-md hover:bg-slate-50 transition cursor-pointer relative z-10\">Schedule Consultation</button></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-slate-950 text-slate-300\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-5 py-14 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] lg:px-8\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-white\"><span class=\"grid size-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-teal-500 text-xl font-black\">✚</span><strong class=\"font-display\">Shifa Global Care</strong></div><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-sm text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Advancing Healthcare. Building Trust. Transforming Lives.<!-- --> We help international patients navigate treatment in India with clarity, dignity, and ongoing support.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Explore</h2><div class=\"mt-4 grid gap-3 text-sm\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/treatments\">Treatments</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/hospitals\">Hospitals</a></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Patient support</h2><div class=\"mt-4 grid gap-3 text-sm\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/medical-visa\">Medical visa</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/faq\">Frequently 